me.dumfing.multiplayerTools

Class ConcurrentGameWorld

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.dumfing.multiplayerTools.ConcurrentGameWorld

  • public class ConcurrentGameWorld
extends java.lang.Object
    A new version of the gameworld that is designed to be used on both the client and serverside for better simulation of how the server's world is working
